Fire Prot. Dist. No. 2 -- 10.53 Mills - BOC - 5 Yrs.
Race.SummaryText:
Fire Protection District No. 2 Proposition
(Millage Renewal)
Race.FullText: Shall Franklin Parish Fire Protection District No. 2, State of Louisiana (the "District"), levy a tax of ten and fifty-three hundredths (10.53) mills on all property subject to taxation in the District (an estimated $126,000 reasonably expected at this time to be collected from the levy of the tax for an entire year), for a period of five (5) years, beginning with the year 2016 and ending with the year 2020, for the purpose of acquiring, constructing, improving, maintaining and operating fire protection facilities and equipment for the District and paying the cost of obtaining water for fire protection purposes?
